metadata.name: 🎂Would you Like to Share a Slice?🎂
metadata.description:
🎂🍓🕯🔪

Cake is a late night delight and guilty pleasure for all. 
'Would You Like to Share a Slice' is my take on a beautiful vintage cake designed in my world! 

🎂Art Created/illustrated by artist Deja Brown🎂 
                 (Deja Doodles/ @dejadoodlesart) 


🎂The owner of this NFT will receive a print!

🎂Please make sure to send me the your email, Twitter, & Instagram account to your profile so I can reach out to you

🎂Single Edition 1/1, Created in 2022
